ncients' and moderns' understanding of Greekness.  a43 0aReligion and statezGreecezThessaly. 0aOxford classical monographs.  aDF 261 T5 M55 2015hUAHS-Bi0162035242690  aDF 261 T5 M55 2015wLCc1i0162035242690d1/28/2017e1/28/2017kCHECKEDOUTlON_SHELFmUAHSSn4p$150.00rMsYtBOOKu2/26/201501ahttp://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/nr2006006871bhttp://viaf.org/viaf/2428932